---
// src/components/Video.astro — demo en vídeo del flujo del TPV
---

<section id="video" class="bg-slate-50 py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Míralo en acción</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Del plano de sala a la cocina y la caja, en unos segundos. Así de fluido funciona en tu restaurante.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-300/40 overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 h-9 bg-slate-100 border-b border-slate-200">
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
        <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-slate-400">Demo del sistema</span>
      </div>
      <video
        src="/video/demo-tpv.mp4"
        poster="/screenshots/plano-sala.webp"
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        preload="none"
        class="w-full h-auto block bg-white"
      ></video>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
